Package: wrappify
Type: Package
Title: An R Wrapper for the Spotify API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Aditya Saluja, Eric Baxter, Luka Vukovic
Maintainer: Eric Baxter <ebaxter271@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides users with a simple means for accessing the
    spotify API using their client credentials. Users can gather information on specific songs, artists,
    or podcasts using either a name or SPotify ID. Functionality is included to recieve information on
    related artists, top songs, recent podcast episodes, and song recomendations given parameters. 
